text:
Nice place here at Kadaloor LRT. Inside with a laundry reception.
Within the place are supermarket, coffee shop, 7-11, hair saloon, cake shop , medical clinic, ATM's, AXS , SAM machine, preschool & waterway primary and Horizon school.
Ang mo super market, 7-eleven, kopitiam, posb and uob aims and some other shops close by
The uncle tending to the mini store is very polite and friendly
